{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21932.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event08","chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"In the end, we made a rule."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"If nothing else, we won't kill anyone based on@vague information."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"We'll only kill people after we've gotten their@name and confirmed their identity."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104301}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_032.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I'm not going to make excuses..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"That man you met, John."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"Do you know what he did?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"He was a low-ranking member of a criminal group,@and an unlucky one, at that..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"He was forced to tag along for a robbery..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"...where he beat a woman to death and shoved@her daughter aside."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"The daughter hit her head and lost consciousness.@She has yet to wake up..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"All of that said..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"...I knew that he wasn't a bad person..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"Do you know how scared he was at the time?"},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"How desperate?"},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I did, because in my dreams, I was the daughter@that he pushed away."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"Every day, for over a month..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"...I would relive \"my\" mother getting killed and@my future being stolen away."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I could tell that he was crying when he shoved@me down."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"He was shaking the whole time..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"But, well..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I stopped caring one morning and wrote his name@on my list."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"That's why Yuu killed him."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"All because I went \"I don't care anymore\"@and put his name down."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"Nothing more, nothing less."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I didn't kill him to save anybody, and I didn't do@it because it was \"right.\""},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I could wring my thoughts for a million different@excuses if I wanted to..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"...but it would be pointless..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_032.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"In some cases..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"...acting as a spokesperson is the furthest thing@from justified, you know?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Shii","textCenter":"I only put names down on my list because of@who \"I\" am and what \"I\" feel."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":390201,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"I got everyone in the orphanage killed..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...yet I am still unable to leave this place."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"I never did get to go somewhere that I could@be free... [chara:390201:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:390201:cheek_0][chara:390201:face_mtn_ex_010.exp3.json:eyeClose_1][chara:390201:lipSynch_1]but that's alright."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":390201,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"I'm choosing to stay trapped of my own volition,@after all."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"Not doing the right thing connects me to Yuu."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"What are your thoughts?"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I..."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390201}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[bgEffect:shakeLarge][flashEffect:flashWhite1]*WHAM!!*","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104301},{"effect":"fadeout","id":390201}],"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"bgm":"bgm24_story05","chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"slideInLeftFast","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":200,"pos":1}]},{"chara":[{"id":390100,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameCenter":"Yuu","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[bgEffect:shakeSmall][chara:390100:effect_shakeModelOffset]W-w-w-wah!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":390100}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","se":"7205_magic_girl","textLeft":"Yuu-san?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"Are we under attack?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":390201},{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_21932.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Nagisa","textLeft":"My ambush was a success...!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Nagisa","textLeft":"Yuu... You're not getting away this time!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
